        <Parent_String>metalworking shears [300023284], metal-cutting and -grinding tools [300162866], equipment for metal-cutting and -grinding [300023221], metalworking equipment [300162819], equipment by material processed [300168082], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
